# SVG & Animation Practice

A collection of SVG elements and animations demonstrating shapes, paths, gradients, and basic motion effects using pure HTML and SVG.

## 📌 Features

- SVG shapes (Circle, Rectangle, Line, Polygon)
- Path-based drawings
- Linear and Radial Gradients
- SVG animations using:
  - <animate>
  - <animateTransform>
- Stroke animation effects
- Opacity animations
- Gradient color transitions

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- SVG
- Built-in SVG Animation

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in any modern browser.
2. Observe animated SVG elements and gradient effects.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Vector graphics using SVG
- Path creation
- Animation properties
- Gradient effects
- Motion and transform animations

